name: com.castsoftware.java.gcp
title: Google Cloud Platform for Java
description: Google Cloud Platform(GCP) is a suite of cloud computing services that runs on the same infrastructure that Google uses internally for its end-user products. Bigtable is a NoSQL database service offered by Google Cloud. Cloud Storage is a service for storing objects in Google Cloud. This extension supports the Google Cloud Bigtable and CloudStorage services for Java
